      <p class="link-style"> A music & film project </p>
      <p class="text">
        "Being part of MusiQ was one of the most creative and carefree period of my life.
        <span id="dots_section_mi2"></span>
        <span class="readMore" id="more_section_mi2">
          James Francis and Roger Jonathxn were collaborating on a music piece, finalized by Darren. After the song was ready, we sat down with Sander Coumou and started brainstorming what scenes of ‘Bonnie’ should have. With Bianca, Michelle and Ross as acting rolls and Jill as the makeup artist, we’ve set the project in motion."
        </span>
